Text: ['Why are you still hesitating?', 'Time never waits.', 'Get started as soon as you can.']
['Well, why do I find it not surprising at all?']

["Go on. Show me what you're capable of.", "Interconnected in purpose, they are the mutual architects of each other's existence.", 'The truth... is hidden within the thread weaved by people.', "Looks like you're a thoughtful one.", 'Impressive.']
['Is this also part of your plan?', 'So the next step is?', 'Hmm...']
['Is it your curiosity that drives you to complete this?', 'Well done, applause to you.', 'Come over. Let me see...']
['Resolve breeds destiny, while hesitation births uncertainty.', 'Your turn.', 'Focus.']
["Let's call it here and leave the rest to our future selves."]
["Don't forget. The last time we met... we were still enemies.", "What a difference... between who you were and who you've become."]
